## Installation
```sh
pip install ColorChalks
```

## Usage       
```python 
from ColorChalks import ColorChalks

# Print "Hello World!" in yellow color.
print(ColorChalks.FCOLORS.Yellow + "Hello World!")
```
**Note:** Version 1.0.2 comes only with foreground colors (FCOLORS)
